text: ( Source : Ireland National Police Service ) 22/10/ 2015 Gardai in Ballina, Co Mayo are investigating a single vehicle fatal road traffic collision that occured at Carrowntreila, Ballina at approximately 6 .30 p.m. yesterday evening the 21st
